    "causal_summary": "HfLocalProvider hardcodes `dtype: 'fp32'` in the `@huggingface/transformers` `pipeline()` call. This forces the largest model variant (~620MB RAM for EmbeddingGemma-300m). The HF cache from 002 contains all dtype variants of the model — `model.onnx` (fp32, default), `model_fp16.onnx`, `model_q4.onnx`, `model_q4f16.onnx`, `model_quantized.onnx` — but the code path never reaches them. RAM and cold-load time are both higher than they need to be.",
